## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="551a7-186">大部分的屬性<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>具有 「 功能 」，結尾的名稱，例如<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.CollationCapability%2A>，是集合的列舉類型的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-186">Most of the properties of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> that have "Capability" at the end of the name, such as <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.CollationCapability%2A>, are collections of values of an enumerated type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="551a7-187">但是<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>和<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>為物件的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-187">But <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A> are collections of objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="551a7-188">為後者的兩個屬性，您無法檢查是否存在特定值的使用**Contains**方法<xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-188">For the latter two properties, you cannot test for the presence of a particular value by using the **Contains** method of <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="551a7-189">這是因為對參考型別，此方法會傳回`true`只有物件的記憶體位址傳遞至時，集合中物件的位址相同，亦即，它們是相同的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-189">This is because, with reference types, the method returns `true` only when the memory address of the object passed to it is the same as the address of an object in the collection; that is, they are the same object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="551a7-190">這通常不是大小寫，因為方法幾乎一定會傳回`false`即使沒有物件集合中具有完全相同的值在其所有屬性的物件傳遞至**Contains**方法 <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-190">Since this will not usually be the case, the method will nearly always return `false` even if there is an object in the collection with exactly the same values in all its properties as the object passed to the **Contains** method of  <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="551a7-191">若要判斷內容<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>，您必須列舉每個成員，比較值與所需的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-191">To determine the contents of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>, you must enumerate through each of its members, comparing them with the desired value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="551a7-192">如果印表機不支援選取的媒體大小而定，集合是空的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-192">If the printer does not support media size selection, the collection is empty.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="551a7-193">此屬性會對應至[列印結構描述](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)的`PageMediaSize`關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-193">This property corresponds to the [Print Schema](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)'s `PageMediaSize` keyword.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="551a7-194">下列程式碼範例示範如何搜尋中的特定值如<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-194">The following code example shows how to search for a particular value in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
foreach (PageMediaSize mediaSize in pc.PageMediaSizeCapability)  
    {  
        if (mediaSize.PageMediaSizeName == PageMediaSizeName.ISOA4)  
        {  
            Console.WriteLine("A4 size is supported");  
            break;  
        }  
    }  
```

  
  
