 <span data-ttu-id="551a7-217"><xref:System.Printing.PageResolution>類別具有您可以在其中指定點每英吋 X 和 Y 維度的屬性和屬性，您可以在其中提供解析度的質化運算式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="551a7-217">The <xref:System.Printing.PageResolution> class has properties in which you can specify the dots-per-inch for the X and Y dimensions and a property where you can give a qualitative expression to the resolution.</span></span>  
  
